name: Eastern Kaio-shin
description: He is one of the Kaio-shin, the gods of creation who are responsible for creating life throughout Universe 7 and protecting it from supreme threats.

originPlanet.name: Core of the World
originPlanet.description: The Core of the World is the native planet of the entire nucleic species, from which the benevolent Kaio and Kaio-shin arise, as well as the malevolent Makaio, Makaio-shin and Demonic Gods in counterpart.
